con:config.script: String TimestampNow, TimestampNextYear log.info TimestampNow = (new Date().time / 1000).intValue() + "000" //current timestamp log.info TimestampNextYear = ((new Date() + 365).time / 1000).intValue() + "000" //timestamp for current time + 365days testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.setPropertyValue("TimestampNow",TimestampNow) testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.setPropertyValue("TimestampNextYear",TimestampNextYear)

def TestPrimaryKeys, TestPrimaryKey, UnitKeys, UnitKey def num = (int)Math.random()*5 //log.info num
TestPrimaryKeys = testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.getPropertyValue( "TestPrimaryKeys" ) log.info TestPrimaryKey = TestPrimaryKeys[1..-2].split(",")[num] testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.setPropertyValue( "TestPrimaryKey", TestPrimaryKey )
UnitKeys = testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.getPropertyValue( "UnitKeys" ) log.info UnitKey = UnitKeys[1..-2].split(",")[4-num] testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.setPropertyValue( "UnitKey", UnitKey )
